cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use EnterpriseSynth, please cite this repository using the metadata below."
title: "EnterpriseSynth"
type: software
version: 0.1.0
date-released: 2026-07-08
abstract: >-
  EnterpriseSynth is a schema-aware agentic framework that ingests OpenAPI/Swagger
  specifications and synthesizes verified Supervised Fine-Tuning (SFT) trajectories and
  evaluation records without executing any live API, targeting the enterprise cold-start
  problem for tool-using LLM agents.
